                  </hi>. I am one of the clerks in the Bloomsbury Branch of the London and Westminster Bank—Mr. Lewis Henry Braham keeps an account there—there was paid in to his account on 5th October last, a 100<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note, 26,188 May 19th, 1860, a 20<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note, 71,853 June 21st, 1860, and another 20<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. note of the same date, No. 71,865.</p>
